posting_body: ['Town Centre', 'Featured Floorplan: 2-bed / 2-bath / 1003 sq ft', 'Monthly Rent: $1635 - $1755', 'Deposit: Call', 'show contact info', "Description: When you rent at Town Centre Apartment Homes, you have easy access to shopping, community events, and Eagan's many attractions.", 'Whether you like the energy of the city, or you prefer to spend your time on the many lakes and rivers in this area, you can do it all from Eagan, MN.', 'Visit Fort Snelling State Park or explore the Mississippi River.', 'Our apartments are also near major employers, the famous Mall of America, the Minneapolis-St. Paul International Airport, and all the amenities the Twin Cities have to offer.', 'Other nearby cities include Bloomington, Woodbury, Mendota Heights, and Minnetonka, MN.', 'Lease Terms: Variable', 'Pet Policy: Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $30.00, Deposit $250.00.', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'Apartment Amenities:', '◾ Air Conditioning', '◾ Ceiling Fans', '◾ Dining Room', '◾ Dishwasher', '◾ Ice Maker In Select Homes', '◾ Intercom/Call Box', '◾ Linen Closet', '◾ Vaulted Ceiling', 'In Select Homes', '◾ Walk-In Closets In Select Homes', '◾ Washer/Dryer Included', 'Community Features:', '◾ Cardio Machines', '◾ Disposal Chutes', '◾ Elevator', '◾ Fitness Center', '◾ Free Weights', '◾ Picnic Area', '◾ Playground', '◾ Recycling', '◾ Smoke-Free', '◾ Views', '◾ 24 Hour Availability', '◾ Barbecue/Grill Area', '◾ Controlled Access Building', '◾ Intercom/Call Box', '◾ Laundry Facilities/Laundry Room', '◾ Off-Street Parking', '◾ On-site Maintenance', '◾ Planned Social Activities', '◾ Reservable Clubhouse', '◾ Volleyball Court', 'Call us:', 'show contact info', '3475 Golfview Dr', 'Eagan, MN 55123', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '7772AB8DCE774080']
